title: Dead of Night
description:
Dead of Night was a horror/mystery anthology title from Marvel in the mid-1970s. It featured a mix of reprints of old Atlas monster stories from Strange Tales, Tales of Suspense and others, including many by Bill Everett, Steve Ditko, and Dick Ayers, plus new stories. Issue #11 featured the debut of the Scarecrow, a weird mystery hero who later went on to headline in Marvel Chillers.


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
